Title: 顶层结构
Describe: Monorepo 目录组织、包管理策略和构建工具链
------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
Monorepo 包结构

[Description]
libs/ 下各包的层级和依赖关系。所有包共享同一个 Git 仓库，但各自独立版本、独立发布。使用 uv workspace 管理本地可编辑依赖。

[UML]
@startuml
left to right direction

package "deepagents/ (monorepo root)" as Root {

  package "libs/" as Libs {
    package "deepagents/\n(SDK core)" as SDK_Pkg {
      component "graph.py" as Graph
      component "backends/" as Backends
      component "middleware/" as MW
      component "profiles/" as Profiles
    }

    package "code/\n(Textual REPL)" as Code_Pkg {
      component "deepagents_code/" as CodeSrc
    }

    package "cli/\n(Deploy tool)" as CLI_Pkg {
      component "deepagents_cli/" as CLISrc
    }

    package "acp/\n(Agent Protocol)" as ACP_Pkg {
      component "deepagents_acp/" as ACPSrc
    }

    package "evals/\n(Eval suite)" as Evals_Pkg {
      component "deepagents_evals/" as EvalSrc
      component "deepagents_harbor/" as Harbor
    }

    package "partners/" as Partners {
      component "daytona/" as Day
      component "modal/" as Mod
      component "quickjs/" as QJS
      component "runloop/" as RL
    }
  }

  package "examples/" as Examples {
  }
}

Code_Pkg --> SDK_Pkg
CLI_Pkg --> SDK_Pkg
ACP_Pkg --> SDK_Pkg
Evals_Pkg --> SDK_Pkg
Partners --> SDK_Pkg
@enduml

[Detail]
**入口点**: 仓库根目录的 `libs/` 包含所有可发布的 Python 包。

**目录约定**:
- 每个包有独立的 `pyproject.toml`、`Makefile`、`tests/`、`CHANGELOG.md`
- 源代码命名规范：`deepagents_xxx/`（下划线分隔，符合 Python 包命名）
- 版本由 `_version.py` + release-please annotation 管理

**依赖方向**（不可违反）:
- 所有包依赖 SDK (`deepagents`)，但 SDK 不依赖任何上层包
- Partner 包通过 `BackendProtocol` 接口与 SDK 解耦
- `examples/` 不属于任何包，仅为演示用途

**版本约束策略**:
- SDK 内部：精确 pin 第三方依赖版本范围
- 上层包对 SDK：范围约束 `>=x.y.0,<(x+1).0.0`
- Code 包例外：精确 pin SDK 版本确保严格兼容

------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
工具链与构建系统

[Description]
uv、ruff、ty、pytest、make 的协作关系。每个工具负责开发流程的一个环节，通过 Makefile 统一入口。

[UML]
None

[Detail]
**工具链速查**:

| 工具 | 职责 | 关键命令 |
|------|------|---------|
| `uv` | 包管理和依赖解析 | `uv sync`, `uv run`, `uv lock` |
| `ruff` | Lint + 格式化 | `make lint`, `make format` |
| `ty` | 静态类型检查 | `ty check` |
| `pytest` | 测试执行 | `make test`, `uv run pytest` |
| `make` | 任务编排 | `make test`, `make bench`, `make lint` |
| `release-please` | 版本管理 | 自动化 PR + CHANGELOG |
| `pre-commit` | 提交钩子 | 格式检查、尾空格、引号修复 |

**Makefile 约定**:
- 每个包根目录有独立的 `Makefile`
- `libs/Makefile` 提供聚合目标（如 `bench-all`）
- CI/CD 直接调用 Makefile targets，保证本地与 CI 行为一致

**开发模式**:
- `[tool.uv.sources]` 配置本地可编辑安装
- 修改 SDK 代码后无需重新安装，上层包立即可见变更
- `uv.lock` 文件锁定精确依赖树，确保可重现构建

------------------------------------------------------------
